SudokuSolver.model

Class PossibleValues

  • java.lang.Object
    • SudokuSolver.model.PossibleValues

  • public class PossibleValues
extends java.lang.Object
    New Possible Values - Creates a list of the Possible Values for each square and uses algorithms to sort sudoku values.

    Gets a list of values for each cell 1-9 It then removes any values from the list that are in the Grid *

    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
